ʔatā mexapēṣ ʔet ha maqōm ha naḳōn ʔēyfo laṣīm
ma qarā
ʔatā rocē še ʔīmaʔ tašīr širīm min ha sēfer
besēder
a ʔatā roʔē ʔīmaʔ ba miṭbāx ba sēfer
ʔīmaʔ ba miṭbāx
ma ʔīmaʔ ʕoṣā ba miṭbāx
ʔīmaʔ ʕomēdet ba miṭbāx we mi ze
Šay ma Šay ʕoṣē
ʔatā rocē še ʔīmaʔ tiqrāʔ sipūr
ʔatā rocē še ʔīmaʔ tiqrāʔ ba sēfer
ʔulāy Liʔōri yedafdēf we yiqrāʔ levād
boʔ nirʔē ma Liʔōri yodēaʕ lehagīd
ma ze
naḳōn
qašqešān
cror maftexōt
ʕaḳšāyw Liʔōr yagīd ma ze
yarōq
ma nigmār
nigmār ha sipūr
loʔ ha sipūr loʔ nigmār raq ha tmunōt nigmerū
ʔo hīne
naḳōn zoʔt Rīna ba tmunā
ma yeš le Rīna ba yadāyim
ʔīmaʔ taʕaṣē ciyūr
loʔ Liʔōri yecayēr levād
ʔatā mevīʔ Liʔōri ʔet ha miṣxāq
ʕaḳšāyw Liʔōri yecayēr ni boʔ
Liʔōri levād loʔ ʔīmaʔ levād
ʔīmaʔ yodāʕat levād ʔatā rocē še ʔīmaʔ tarʔē leḳā
